nodes.body: @epananth do these changes have our 16.10 V2 channel, or do we need to wait for another version bump?

I don't see my commit in this yet. So I would hold off on merging this PR. Probably the next update will have my change, ( as this was created around 5;30 pm on 1/29 and I created that PR around 9 pm on 1/29)

Also I see commits from last October. Since it was using older arcade is that the reason for no arcade update?

Sounds good, closing this one.

We haven't been taking many arcade updates since we started working on the arcade 5 upgrade (which later turned into a net5.0 upgrade). 

Also because we were on 1.0 we prioritized updates that would fix our builds.
